1. *Pošto* je rano proleće, temperatura je niska. (Since it is early spring, the temperature is low.)

2. Ona je već odavno *pošto* je završila fakultet. (She has been finished with university for a long time now.)

3. *Pošto* je sveobuhvatna tema, potrebno je mnogo vremena da se nauči. (Since it is a comprehensive topic, it takes a lot of time to learn it.)

4. *Pošto* ne želim da se zakasnim, rano se probudim. (Since I don't want to be late, I wake up early.)

5. *Pošto* je došao rano, bio je prvi čovek u redu. (Since he arrived early, he was the first person in line.)